Jeff Wicks, News24(iStock) Multimedia &nbsp; &nbsp; User Galleries &nbsp; &nbsp; News in Pictures Send us your pictures &nbsp; &nbsp; Send us your stories Three arrested and one injured in Sandton shootout.WATCHDurban - A suspected robber is&nbsp;under police guard in hospital&nbsp;after a dramatic shoot-out with security guards in Westmead, Pinetown, in the early hours of Wednesday morning. &nbsp; Blue Security operations manager Brian Jackson said a gang of seven robbers had held up two security guards stationed&nbsp;at the premises of a business in Ficus Place shortly before 04:00. "When our officer arrived on the scene a suspect came out of the guard room and fired several shots at him. He [the officer] returned fire before calling for backup. The suspect fled the scene," he said. "Our officer investigated further and found a security guard handcuffed inside the guard room and a second suspect, who had been shot earlier by the second security guard, lying injured at the back of the&nbsp;property."Paramedics transported the injured suspect to hospital. Jackson said the&nbsp;robbers managed to get away&nbsp;with computers.24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.